Description: 1 fragment of papyrus with demotic agreement on front, written in columns, from Soknopaiou Nesos (Dime) in the Fayum.
Curator's comments: A demotic agreement from Soknopaiou Nesos in the Fayum from the Roman period, studied with a view to publication of pBM EA 76170-3 by Maren Schentuleit (Oxford) and Sandra Lippert (Paris) [ERO 2022].
